<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>CSS Box Example</title>

<style>
body {
    background-color: lightblue;
}

.box {
    width: 300px;
    height: 200px;
    background-color: white;
    border: 3px solid black;
    margin: 50px auto;
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
}

h2 {
    color: red;
}

p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: darkgreen;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="box">
<h2>CSS Box</h2>
<p>This is another CSS program example.</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>